OBJECTIVES: I.

 Conduct a randomized, double blind, placebo controlled, parallel study of the atypical neuroleptic risperidone (RIS) in the treatment of children and adults with moderate to severe Tourette Syndrome.

 II.

 Evaluate further the safety of RIS in this population.

